270
00:29:09,000 --> 00:29:11,000
[SPEAKER_02] Pridobili.

271
00:29:11,000 --> 00:29:12,000
[SPEAKER_02] Pridobili.

272
00:29:12,000 --> 00:29:19,000
[SPEAKER_02] Pridobili, od njih sam imao baš dobar osjećaj da će to biti dobro.

273
00:29:19,000 --> 00:29:21,000
