303
00:33:06,000 --> 00:33:09,000
[SPEAKER_02] Mislim da je ovo sve šta se dešava sada lajk.

304
00:33:09,000 --> 00:33:11,000
[SPEAKER_02] Ovo je lajk.

305
00:33:11,000 --> 00:33:12,000
[SPEAKER_02] Ovo je lajk.

306
00:33:12,000 --> 00:33:20,000
